<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es" class="transition-colors duration-300 dark">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>¡Registro exitoso! - MusicVibe</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fda4af, #ffffff, #fbcfe8);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 px-4">
  <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full max-w-md p-8">
    <a href="/" class="flex justify-center items-center mb-4">
      <img src="/assets/img/IconNoBGB.png" alt="Logo" class="h-32 w-auto">
    </a>
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-center text-pink-700 dark:text-pink-400 mb-4">
      ¡Gracias por registrarte, <%= nombre %>!
    </h2>
    <div class="mb-6">
      <p class="text-center text-lg font-semibold text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">
        Te has registrado con el correo: <strong><%= email %></strong>
      </p>
      <p class="text-center text-base mt-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        ¡Ya puedes iniciar sesión y empezar a disfrutar de MusicVibe!
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
      <a href="/login"
        class="w-full bg-pink-700 hover:bg-pink-600 text-white font-semibold py-2 rounded-md transition shadow-md text-center">
        Ir al Login
      </a>
      <a href="/"
        class="w-full bg-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-700 dark:hover:bg-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 font-semibold py-2 rounded-md transition shadow-md text-center">
        Ir a la página de inicio
      </a>
    </div>
    <p class="text-xs text-center mt-8 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
      &copy; <span id="year"><script>document.getElementById('year').textContent = new Date().getFullYear();</script></span> MusicVibe
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
